  "title": "Office Cleaner",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a reliable <strong>Office Cleaner</strong> to maintain a clean, safe, and hygienic work environment. This role is suitable for individuals who are responsible, detail-oriented, and able to work independently.</p><p>Training will be provided for all cleaning procedures and equipment.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Clean and maintain office floors, furniture, and common areas</p></li><li><p>Empty trash bins and dispose of waste properly</p></li><li><p>Ensure restrooms are clean, stocked, and hygienic</p></li><li><p>Replenish office supplies as needed (e.g., tissue, soap)</p></li><li><p>Report any maintenance or repair issues promptly</p></li><li><p>Follow cleaning schedules and safety guidelines</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 18 years old</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate in basic English</p></li><li><p>Responsible, punctual, and reliable</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently or as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Prior cleaning experience is a plus but not required</p></li></ul>",
